@sly92: That "weird mustache" you're referring to ... that wouldn't happen to be its mouth?  

And regarding the art, I like it. It's a twisted abomination with no heart (at least I'm pretty sure), which is why it looks so weird and has that hole in its chest.  
Another thing I like about The Unspeakable is that it can pick up [Reach Through Mists](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Reach Through Mists), [Peer Through Depths](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Peer Through Depths) and [Sift Through Sands](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Sift Through Sands) from your graveyard again once you start swining, which can be pretty useful in case your opponent decides to aim removal at its face.
